WEBVTT


00:00:08.321 --> 00:00:10.031
-Euneo.
-Yes, euneo.

00:00:11.199 --> 00:00:13.827
Oh, euneo. Sweetfish.

00:00:13.910 --> 00:00:14.744
Sweetfish.

00:00:14.828 --> 00:00:17.413
-Sweetfish. Euneo.
-Euneo.

00:00:17.497 --> 00:00:18.331
Yes, got it.

00:00:18.414 --> 00:00:20.333
He's a nice kid.

00:00:22.669 --> 00:00:24.045
You think so?

00:00:24.129 --> 00:00:26.381
Isn't that why you brought him here?

00:00:26.464 --> 00:00:29.926
I mean, he just showed up in Japan.

00:00:30.426 --> 00:00:32.137
Isn't that great?

00:00:33.388 --> 00:00:35.807
It feels livelier with him around.

00:00:36.933 --> 00:00:38.810
And your father looks so happy.

00:00:39.310 --> 00:00:41.020
They totally hit it off.

00:00:41.104 --> 00:00:41.938
Here.

00:00:44.566 --> 00:00:47.110
-Yeah, it's good.
-Good.

00:00:48.361 --> 00:00:53.283
He may not show it,
but your father was worried about you.

00:00:53.366 --> 00:00:54.659
He must be relieved.

00:00:57.412 --> 00:00:58.371
Sorry.

00:01:01.875 --> 00:01:06.671
It's a parent's job to worry,
even when there's nothing wrong.

00:01:13.136 --> 00:01:15.972
Hey. How's school?

00:01:16.890 --> 00:01:21.561
All you ever did was play ice hockey,
so you must have trouble studying.

00:01:21.644 --> 00:01:24.564
I'll graduate, at the very least.

00:01:24.647 --> 00:01:26.774
You don't have to push yourself.

00:01:27.525 --> 00:01:29.485
It's okay if you want to quit.

00:01:30.612 --> 00:01:32.030
More importantly,

00:01:33.156 --> 00:01:34.991
come visit us again.

00:01:37.160 --> 00:01:38.953
And bring Johan with you.

00:01:40.330 --> 00:01:43.583
But he's gonna serve in the military soon.

00:01:43.666 --> 00:01:44.751
What?

00:01:44.834 --> 00:01:47.295
Ryeowook is going soon too, you know.

00:01:47.378 --> 00:01:50.089
I was a pretty big fan of his.

00:01:50.173 --> 00:01:52.550
What? You listen to that stuff?

00:01:53.343 --> 00:01:56.429
I listen. I sing.

00:01:56.512 --> 00:01:58.097
I can dance too!

00:02:09.525 --> 00:02:10.735
Is it okay

00:02:12.237 --> 00:02:14.364
if I stay lost in Tokyo a bit longer?

00:02:18.034 --> 00:02:20.161
Stay lost to your heart's content.

00:02:26.334 --> 00:02:27.669
Hey, do you eat mushrooms?

00:02:27.752 --> 00:02:29.629
-Huh? What?
-Mushrooms.

00:02:29.712 --> 00:02:32.090
-Oh, I do.
-The nimono is ready too.

00:02:32.173 --> 00:02:33.925
Now, let's eat!

00:02:34.008 --> 00:02:36.552
Wait, you're already eating.

00:02:36.636 --> 00:02:37.512
All right.

00:02:37.595 --> 00:02:39.472
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

00:02:39.555 --> 00:02:42.183
-Geonbae!
-Geonbae!

00:02:44.477 --> 00:02:48.022
Eat some veggies. Here, go ahead.

00:02:55.989 --> 00:02:57.490
Hey, don't touch it.

00:02:58.825 --> 00:03:00.201
You'll get burned.

00:03:00.827 --> 00:03:02.328
-A flower!
-Don't play around!

00:03:02.412 --> 00:03:05.248
Draw a circle, then a flower!

00:03:09.085 --> 00:03:10.211
-Hey.
-Oh.

00:03:10.295 --> 00:03:11.337
You scared me.

00:03:17.218 --> 00:03:18.428
Should we join them?

00:03:21.597 --> 00:03:22.765
Wow!

00:03:23.975 --> 00:03:26.227
-Here, the bucket!
-Put it there.

00:03:30.231 --> 00:03:31.190
Whoa.

00:03:32.275 --> 00:03:34.986
Wow! The smoke!

00:03:35.069 --> 00:03:36.237
It's hot!

00:03:36.321 --> 00:03:38.114
Be careful! It's dangerous!

00:03:38.197 --> 00:03:39.407
Watch it!

00:03:45.288 --> 00:03:46.622
Want me to wash your back?

00:03:47.123 --> 00:03:48.041
Hmm?

00:03:48.124 --> 00:03:49.167
Your back.

00:03:50.960 --> 00:03:51.961
Okay.

00:03:53.671 --> 00:03:54.672
Here.

00:04:00.428 --> 00:04:05.600
Your uncle's paintings were really good.

00:04:06.851 --> 00:04:07.727
Yeah.

00:04:07.810 --> 00:04:11.773
I'll never forget your uncle's paintings

00:04:13.358 --> 00:04:15.109
or everything we did today.

00:04:16.569 --> 00:04:18.279
What are you talking about?

00:04:25.286 --> 00:04:26.621
Thank you.

00:04:32.585 --> 00:04:33.586
Sure.

00:04:38.591 --> 00:04:39.592
Yeah.

00:05:06.119 --> 00:05:07.662
Thank you very much.

00:05:08.413 --> 00:05:09.455
Come by again, okay?

00:05:09.539 --> 00:05:10.540
I will.

00:05:12.583 --> 00:05:13.626
Abeoji.

00:05:14.502 --> 00:05:15.545
Eomeoni.

00:05:21.300 --> 00:05:22.385
Bye, then.

00:05:22.468 --> 00:05:23.469
Okay.

00:05:25.805 --> 00:05:27.140
-Here.
-Oh.

00:05:27.807 --> 00:05:30.768
Let's go fishing next time.

00:05:31.936 --> 00:05:33.479
-Definitely.
-Yeah.

00:05:33.980 --> 00:05:35.440
Keep in touch.

00:05:36.566 --> 00:05:38.151
See you again!

00:05:38.234 --> 00:05:39.318
Now, now.

00:05:58.880 --> 00:06:00.339
-Take care, okay?
-Okay.

00:06:00.423 --> 00:06:01.966
-I'll keep in touch.
-Okay!

00:06:02.049 --> 00:06:03.926
Come by again!

00:06:04.010 --> 00:06:05.136
Euneo!

00:06:05.720 --> 00:06:06.971
Sweetfish!

00:06:21.277 --> 00:06:24.155
Next time, give me a heads-up
before you come visit, okay?

00:06:24.989 --> 00:06:26.032
Next time?

00:06:26.115 --> 00:06:27.116
Yeah.

00:06:29.368 --> 00:06:33.414
It's your turn to come visit me next time.

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:37.668
-That's true.
-Yeah.

00:06:48.513 --> 00:06:49.514
What was that?

00:07:13.412 --> 00:07:14.997
Hmm?

00:07:15.581 --> 00:07:17.333
-You suck.
-What?

00:07:18.918 --> 00:07:20.586
It looks exactly like you.

00:07:22.004 --> 00:07:23.631
-Exactly like me?
-Yeah.

00:07:43.776 --> 00:07:49.156
TRAINING ELITE FORCES WHO FIGHT AND WIN

00:08:00.209 --> 00:08:01.085
Hello?

00:08:01.168 --> 00:08:03.879
Hello? It's, uh…

00:08:03.963 --> 00:08:04.964
Yeah?

00:08:05.798 --> 00:08:08.009
Coach got a call.

00:08:09.260 --> 00:08:10.428
Arata is…

00:08:23.357 --> 00:08:24.442
Come in.

00:08:45.504 --> 00:08:46.505
Hey.

00:09:05.358 --> 00:09:06.901
Why don't you sit?

00:09:06.984 --> 00:09:07.985
Okay.

00:09:28.839 --> 00:09:30.257
Long time no see.

00:09:31.300 --> 00:09:33.844
You're saying that now?

00:09:35.137 --> 00:09:36.222
True.

00:09:41.310 --> 00:09:43.145
You came by a lot, didn't you?

00:09:50.695 --> 00:09:51.779
Hey.

00:09:58.119 --> 00:09:59.537
About back then…

00:10:03.499 --> 00:10:04.375
I'm sorry.

00:10:04.458 --> 00:10:06.544
Whoa, stop.

00:10:08.003 --> 00:10:09.004
Wait.

00:10:11.006 --> 00:10:12.007
What?

00:10:15.428 --> 00:10:17.012
Are you here to apologize?

00:10:20.266 --> 00:10:21.267
I…

00:10:23.728 --> 00:10:24.937
When that happened…

00:10:29.442 --> 00:10:31.318
I couldn't protect you.

00:10:31.402 --> 00:10:33.154
I don't need that from you.

00:10:33.237 --> 00:10:36.449
I never thought you failed to protect me.

00:10:38.242 --> 00:10:39.618
It is what it is.

00:10:41.454 --> 00:10:44.665
I'll admit I didn't think
it would go around like that.

00:10:49.170 --> 00:10:50.880
But what could we do?

00:10:53.132 --> 00:10:55.551
You were simply protecting yourself.

00:10:59.388 --> 00:11:00.556
But that's why--

00:11:00.639 --> 00:11:03.517
I was prepared for that.

00:11:08.022 --> 00:11:10.191
I was fully aware of what might happen…

00:11:14.278 --> 00:11:16.197
when I confessed my feelings to you.

00:11:19.867 --> 00:11:22.077
I wanted you to know

00:11:23.996 --> 00:11:25.080
how I felt.

00:11:29.043 --> 00:11:34.089
If, right now

00:11:35.090 --> 00:11:41.639
I can be true to my feelings

00:11:55.319 --> 00:11:56.195
Are you ready?

00:11:56.278 --> 00:11:57.696
-Yeah.
-Okay.

00:12:00.115 --> 00:12:02.201
I'm sorry it's heavy.

00:12:02.284 --> 00:12:03.285
It's fine.

00:12:06.038 --> 00:12:07.248
Go on ahead.

00:12:07.331 --> 00:12:08.415
Sure.

00:12:11.043 --> 00:12:12.002
Thanks.

00:12:12.086 --> 00:12:13.087
No worries.

00:12:52.084 --> 00:12:57.464
My admiration

00:12:57.548 --> 00:13:02.678
And my love

00:13:04.096 --> 00:13:08.601
Will fly to the wide open sky

00:13:09.393 --> 00:13:15.941
And shine brightly

00:13:16.942 --> 00:13:22.281
I believe in future

00:13:23.240 --> 00:13:27.411
I believe

00:13:33.542 --> 00:13:35.336
All firing lines, firing complete!

00:13:47.681 --> 00:13:48.682
Keep a straight line!

00:13:48.766 --> 00:13:51.018
Keep a straight line!

00:13:54.563 --> 00:13:55.564
Johan.

00:13:57.191 --> 00:13:58.859
Give these a proper polish.

00:13:58.943 --> 00:14:00.569
Polish mine too.

00:14:00.653 --> 00:14:02.321
Do mine too.

00:14:03.572 --> 00:14:05.866
Being an ex-boxer goes to your head, huh?

00:14:05.950 --> 00:14:08.243
Don't get cocky.

00:14:09.495 --> 00:14:10.829
Troops, halt!

00:14:20.255 --> 00:14:22.675
Time's moving so slow.

00:14:23.342 --> 00:14:24.760
And you call this food?

00:14:28.013 --> 00:14:30.099
My youth is like a piece of shit.

00:14:35.437 --> 00:14:38.857
At times like these…

00:14:41.110 --> 00:14:43.529
think about the fun times you've had.

00:14:46.407 --> 00:14:47.950
The fun times?

00:14:48.867 --> 00:14:49.868
Yeah.

00:14:50.577 --> 00:14:53.831
Or about the fun times
that are bound to come.

00:14:59.128 --> 00:15:00.254
Welcome.

00:15:04.883 --> 00:15:06.301
-Yo.
-Hey.

00:15:08.721 --> 00:15:10.431
How was the interview?

00:15:10.514 --> 00:15:13.058
Man, it was a total bust.

00:15:13.142 --> 00:15:15.019
It felt like it went nowhere.

00:15:15.102 --> 00:15:17.813
-Please put your bags in here.
-Thank you.

00:15:18.522 --> 00:15:20.441
-Anyway, good work.
-Thanks.

00:15:21.358 --> 00:15:23.402
You're so lucky.

00:15:23.485 --> 00:15:25.738
You already landed a job
through connections.

00:15:25.821 --> 00:15:26.947
I guess so.

00:15:27.448 --> 00:15:31.285
Still, it kind of sucks
not getting to choose for myself.

00:15:31.368 --> 00:15:33.287
I feel a bit conflicted about it.

00:15:33.370 --> 00:15:35.539
My job was decided automatically.

00:15:35.622 --> 00:15:37.458
That's what makes me jealous.

00:15:38.208 --> 00:15:39.460
What about your hometown?

00:15:39.543 --> 00:15:41.545
You could take over your dad's business.

00:15:41.628 --> 00:15:43.881
No, I don't think that's happening.

00:15:43.964 --> 00:15:45.674
I see.

00:15:46.300 --> 00:15:48.052
-Some beer?
-Yeah.

00:15:49.053 --> 00:15:50.804
Thanks.

00:15:53.182 --> 00:15:54.266
All right.

00:15:54.349 --> 00:15:55.934
Let's drink.

00:15:56.018 --> 00:15:56.935
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

00:16:02.816 --> 00:16:03.734
That's good.

00:16:03.817 --> 00:16:05.652
-That hits the spot.
-Yeah.

00:16:07.488 --> 00:16:10.074
What should we eat today?

00:16:10.657 --> 00:16:12.409
I'm definitely getting the tongue.

00:16:15.704 --> 00:16:16.663
Hello?

00:16:16.747 --> 00:16:19.166
-Hello? Ryu?
-Yeah.

00:16:19.249 --> 00:16:22.544
Hey, I think I'm close by now, but…

00:16:22.628 --> 00:16:25.297
Yeah? Okay, got it.

00:16:25.380 --> 00:16:27.299
I'll come outside then.

00:16:27.841 --> 00:16:28.884
-Thanks.
-Sure.

00:16:28.967 --> 00:16:30.094
I think I'm here!

00:16:30.177 --> 00:16:31.637
-Oh, Ryu!
-Hey!

00:16:31.720 --> 00:16:34.348
-You found it?
-Yeah, just barely.

00:16:34.431 --> 00:16:35.724
-I'll take that.
-Thanks.

00:16:35.808 --> 00:16:38.519
-Of course.
-I'm so glad I made it.

00:16:40.145 --> 00:16:42.397
-Good evening.
-Good evening. I'll take these.

00:16:42.481 --> 00:16:45.400
-Thank you. Sorry for the trouble.
-Thank you.

00:16:45.484 --> 00:16:47.402
I'm sorry I'm late.

00:16:47.486 --> 00:16:49.363
This is Sumiko, who I told you about.

00:16:49.863 --> 00:16:52.032
H-Hello! I'm Super Scrappy Seiichi!

00:16:53.826 --> 00:16:54.660
"Super Scrappy"?

00:16:54.743 --> 00:16:56.537
We played ice hockey together. He's Sei--

00:16:56.620 --> 00:16:58.205
Seiichi.

00:16:59.498 --> 00:17:01.625
-Nice to meet you.
-Nice to meet you too.

00:17:02.334 --> 00:17:03.919
-Please have a seat.
-Okay.

00:17:04.002 --> 00:17:05.212
What's with this guy?

00:17:05.295 --> 00:17:09.091
It's amazing that you went abroad
right out of high school.

00:17:09.174 --> 00:17:11.301
It's like, you take initiative.

00:17:11.385 --> 00:17:13.428
Anyway, it's really cool.

00:17:15.722 --> 00:17:20.269
My parents are divorced,
and my family situation is complicated.

00:17:20.352 --> 00:17:23.397
I'm pretty much estranged from my mother,

00:17:23.480 --> 00:17:26.358
so part of me was like,
"I need a job quick!"

00:17:27.109 --> 00:17:31.697
So, I secretly borrowed money
from my dad, who lives separately.

00:17:32.197 --> 00:17:35.033
That makes you even cooler.

00:17:35.534 --> 00:17:38.245
All we had was ice hockey, huh?

00:17:38.328 --> 00:17:40.372
You have your parents' connections too.

00:17:40.455 --> 00:17:41.790
Shut up.

00:17:41.874 --> 00:17:44.334
Here, Sumiko. Eat this.

00:17:44.418 --> 00:17:46.044
Thank you.

00:17:46.879 --> 00:17:48.213
So good!

00:17:49.798 --> 00:17:51.550
-Oh, hey.
-Yeah?

00:17:51.633 --> 00:17:55.762
Do you have
hair conditioner at your place?

00:17:57.139 --> 00:17:57.973
Nope.

00:17:58.056 --> 00:18:01.518
Right? I'm so glad I asked.
I'll get some on the way back.

00:18:01.602 --> 00:18:03.770
I'm a guy living alone, so…

00:18:03.854 --> 00:18:05.856
-Um…
-I might be missing some stuff.

00:18:05.939 --> 00:18:07.316
May I?

00:18:07.399 --> 00:18:08.483
Hmm?

00:18:08.567 --> 00:18:10.652
So, um…

00:18:11.153 --> 00:18:14.740
Are you staying at Ryu's place, Sumiko?

00:18:14.823 --> 00:18:16.325
Yeah, I am.

00:18:16.408 --> 00:18:20.120
That's where I'm staying for now
until I find my own place in Tokyo.

00:18:20.204 --> 00:18:21.205
What?

00:18:22.206 --> 00:18:23.707
What? Uh…

00:18:24.208 --> 00:18:27.628
Hmm, but is that really okay?

00:18:28.170 --> 00:18:30.005
There's nothing going on between us.

00:18:30.088 --> 00:18:31.089
Yeah.

00:18:31.173 --> 00:18:33.425
But…

00:18:33.508 --> 00:18:34.509
I know!

00:18:35.093 --> 00:18:38.263
Maybe I'll stay over at your place too.

00:18:38.347 --> 00:18:39.389
What?!

00:18:39.473 --> 00:18:40.515
We're here.

00:18:40.599 --> 00:18:41.808
Which floor, Ryu?

00:18:41.892 --> 00:18:43.101
-Second floor.
-Second?

00:18:43.185 --> 00:18:44.019
That's fine.

00:18:44.102 --> 00:18:45.646
I'm okay. Go ahead.

00:18:46.146 --> 00:18:48.273
-Can you make it?
-I'm fine. I work out.

00:18:48.357 --> 00:18:49.691
-You're sweating!
-I'm not.

00:18:49.775 --> 00:18:51.276
You work out?

00:18:51.360 --> 00:18:54.738
There we go! I'm fine. Leave it to me.

00:18:54.821 --> 00:18:55.989
You can do it, Seiichi!

00:18:56.073 --> 00:18:57.241
I told you, I'm fine.

00:18:57.324 --> 00:18:58.909
-All right.
-Here, Sumiko.

00:18:58.992 --> 00:19:00.994
-Oh, thanks.
-I'll bring this inside.

00:19:01.078 --> 00:19:02.079
Are you good?

00:19:02.162 --> 00:19:03.580
Phew.

00:19:06.250 --> 00:19:08.168
Whoa.

00:19:08.877 --> 00:19:10.629
You're really living alone!

00:19:10.712 --> 00:19:11.672
I sure am.

00:19:11.755 --> 00:19:13.298
You keep it pretty clean.

00:19:13.382 --> 00:19:14.383
Yeah, I guess.

00:19:20.097 --> 00:19:22.724
Wait, are you interested in caregiving?

00:19:22.808 --> 00:19:25.936
Not seriously or anything. Just a little.

00:19:26.520 --> 00:19:27.354
I'll take these.

00:19:27.437 --> 00:19:30.357
-Thanks.
-Man, I could never handle it.

00:19:31.191 --> 00:19:33.860
What you can't handle
is that strict caregiver.

00:19:33.944 --> 00:19:35.195
Shut up.

00:19:35.862 --> 00:19:37.739
-Oh! Sumiko.
-Hm?

00:19:37.823 --> 00:19:38.949
Sit here.

00:19:39.032 --> 00:19:40.158
-Okay.
-Yeah.

00:19:40.242 --> 00:19:42.744
-Come. Over here.
-Thank you.

00:19:44.454 --> 00:19:45.455
-UNO!
-What?

00:19:45.539 --> 00:19:48.000
-Wait a minute. Oh, no.
-This is bad!

00:19:48.083 --> 00:19:48.917
Hold on.

00:19:49.001 --> 00:19:52.004
-Please let me win!
-Wait, what should I do?

00:19:52.087 --> 00:19:53.922
-Come on!
-Here. I'll play this.

00:19:54.006 --> 00:19:55.048
What?

00:19:55.132 --> 00:19:57.384
-Come on!
-I don't have any. Oh, this one.

00:19:57.467 --> 00:19:59.177
I'm gonna take this call.

00:19:59.261 --> 00:20:00.345
Huh?

00:20:00.429 --> 00:20:03.265
Wait. You can't run away
because you're about to lose.

00:20:03.348 --> 00:20:04.850
That's not what I'm doing.

00:20:05.559 --> 00:20:06.893
You guys keep playing.

00:20:13.275 --> 00:20:14.609
Hello?

00:20:15.110 --> 00:20:17.070
Did Sumiko arrive?

00:20:17.154 --> 00:20:18.155
Yeah.

00:20:18.947 --> 00:20:21.033
We were playing UNO just now.

00:20:21.658 --> 00:20:23.994
Huh? "Uno"?

00:20:24.578 --> 00:20:25.579
UNO.

00:20:26.163 --> 00:20:27.831
Wait, don't you have UNO in Korea?

00:20:29.458 --> 00:20:30.459
"Uno."

00:20:31.168 --> 00:20:33.003
Oh, sweetfish.

00:20:35.172 --> 00:20:36.965
No, not that.

00:20:37.049 --> 00:20:38.759
Um, how do I put this?

00:20:39.259 --> 00:20:41.136
It's the name of a card game.

00:20:42.095 --> 00:20:43.305
Oh.

00:20:45.724 --> 00:20:46.767
Damn.

00:20:47.476 --> 00:20:50.520
Now I want to eat Abeoji's euneo.

00:20:51.563 --> 00:20:53.023
I'll let him know.

00:20:53.982 --> 00:20:55.776
I want to eat it right now.

00:20:57.110 --> 00:20:58.111
Yeah.

00:20:58.779 --> 00:21:00.614
After my military service ends,

00:21:02.324 --> 00:21:07.996
I've decided to become a coach
at my coach's gym for now.

00:21:08.997 --> 00:21:10.499
Oh, I see.

00:21:12.376 --> 00:21:13.877
That's good.

00:21:14.669 --> 00:21:16.880
Yeah, I'm relieved.

00:21:18.465 --> 00:21:19.674
Good luck.

00:21:21.051 --> 00:21:22.719
Tell me if I'm wrong.

00:21:23.387 --> 00:21:28.058
Are you and Ryu, by any chance…

00:21:29.726 --> 00:21:31.686
Of course not.

00:21:34.689 --> 00:21:35.899
Is that so?

00:21:36.483 --> 00:21:38.902
Well, that makes sense.

00:21:39.694 --> 00:21:40.695
Sorry about that.

00:21:40.779 --> 00:21:44.157
No, there's no need to apologize.

00:21:45.200 --> 00:21:46.326
Sorry.

00:21:47.577 --> 00:21:48.787
What about you?

00:21:48.870 --> 00:21:50.622
Is there anyone you like?

00:21:51.248 --> 00:21:53.834
Huh? Oh.

00:21:53.917 --> 00:21:55.669
Hmm…

00:21:56.628 --> 00:22:01.049
No, I don't… Well, maybe I do.

00:22:01.133 --> 00:22:03.093
What?

00:22:03.176 --> 00:22:04.719
What was that?

00:22:04.803 --> 00:22:06.721
Who is it? Someone from school?

00:22:06.805 --> 00:22:08.056
Are you guys going out?

00:22:08.140 --> 00:22:11.017
Oh, no. We're not.

00:22:11.101 --> 00:22:12.519
-Oh?
-Yeah.

00:22:12.602 --> 00:22:14.646
I don't have a girlfriend.

00:22:14.729 --> 00:22:18.275
I see. What does she do?

00:22:18.775 --> 00:22:20.402
Um…

00:22:24.156 --> 00:22:27.492
She might be drinking.

00:22:27.576 --> 00:22:30.036
Oh? So, she likes to drink.

00:22:33.290 --> 00:22:37.669
And she might be eating potato chips.

00:22:41.423 --> 00:22:42.424
Huh?

00:22:44.843 --> 00:22:45.844
Huh?

00:22:51.892 --> 00:22:55.437
A love at first sight… kind of thing.

00:22:57.647 --> 00:22:59.065
Oh…

00:23:00.567 --> 00:23:01.735
Um…

00:23:04.488 --> 00:23:08.074
Let's start off as friends… kind of thing.

00:23:09.159 --> 00:23:10.327
Right.

00:23:10.952 --> 00:23:17.959
Like, we take it step by step,
then you make a final call kind of thing?

00:23:23.131 --> 00:23:24.633
Whoa!

00:23:25.133 --> 00:23:28.762
-What are you doing, Ryu?
-Hey. Come on!

00:23:28.845 --> 00:23:30.096
What the hell?

00:23:30.180 --> 00:23:32.140
-You're so freaked out.
-That scared me.

00:23:32.224 --> 00:23:34.476
What is it, huh?

00:23:34.559 --> 00:23:36.937
Come on, stop messing with me!

00:23:37.020 --> 00:23:38.438
What were you talking about?

00:23:38.522 --> 00:23:40.732
Nothing.

00:23:40.815 --> 00:23:42.984
-Jeez. Come on.
-Yeah?

00:23:43.068 --> 00:23:44.611
Let's play UNO.

00:23:44.694 --> 00:23:46.821
Huh? You guys weren't playing?

00:23:46.905 --> 00:23:48.532
Well, you ran away.

00:23:57.499 --> 00:23:58.708
Attention!

00:23:59.626 --> 00:24:01.336
Salute your superiors!

00:24:01.419 --> 00:24:02.879
Loyalty!

00:24:02.963 --> 00:24:03.964
Loyalty!

00:24:04.464 --> 00:24:06.383
Take care! We're going now.

00:24:06.466 --> 00:24:07.634
Thank you for your service.

00:24:11.888 --> 00:24:13.223
Dad!

00:24:15.892 --> 00:24:18.144
How have you been?

00:24:52.929 --> 00:24:54.764
Good work.

00:24:56.433 --> 00:24:58.518
I bet you're super buff now, huh?

00:24:59.019 --> 00:25:01.021
I was already buff.

00:25:03.440 --> 00:25:05.108
It's finally over.

00:25:05.191 --> 00:25:06.484
Yeah.

00:25:07.152 --> 00:25:08.361
I'm glad.

00:25:09.237 --> 00:25:11.448
Yeah. I'm glad too.

00:25:11.948 --> 00:25:14.492
Anyway, I've got my plane ticket
for next week.

00:25:15.160 --> 00:25:17.537
You better clean your house properly.

00:25:17.621 --> 00:25:18.622
Okay.

00:25:22.250 --> 00:25:23.835
I got paged. I'm gonna go.

00:25:23.918 --> 00:25:25.211
I'll call you again.

00:25:25.295 --> 00:25:26.880
Oh, okay. Bye.

00:25:26.963 --> 00:25:28.340
Yep. Annyeong.

00:25:54.032 --> 00:25:55.450
We're not open yet--

00:25:55.533 --> 00:25:56.368
Ta-da!

00:25:56.451 --> 00:25:59.913
Oh! You're alive?

00:26:00.538 --> 00:26:03.166
Don't kill me off like that.

00:26:03.249 --> 00:26:04.417
I'm just kidding.

00:26:04.918 --> 00:26:06.544
Hold on a second.

00:26:08.421 --> 00:26:10.799
I've been saving something for you.

00:26:10.882 --> 00:26:12.550
What is it?

00:26:12.634 --> 00:26:13.843
Just wait.

00:26:17.180 --> 00:26:18.682
Ta-da!

00:26:18.765 --> 00:26:20.308
Isn't that expensive?

00:26:20.392 --> 00:26:21.893
It is.

00:26:25.480 --> 00:26:26.981
Welcome back from prison.

00:26:27.065 --> 00:26:28.817
I was discharged from the military.

00:26:36.616 --> 00:26:37.867
What about the soda?

00:26:37.951 --> 00:26:39.869
You drink expensive liquor neat.

00:26:41.121 --> 00:26:42.122
Cheers.

00:26:42.997 --> 00:26:43.998
Cheers.

00:27:19.701 --> 00:27:21.453
Hey, Hyeong.

00:27:21.536 --> 00:27:23.538
Wow, this place is great.

00:27:23.621 --> 00:27:25.707
Sorry, we're not open yet.

00:27:25.790 --> 00:27:29.961
What? That guy's a customer. Are we not?

00:27:30.044 --> 00:27:32.130
Hey, sit.

00:27:32.213 --> 00:27:34.257
Are you discriminating against us?

00:27:36.509 --> 00:27:37.677
I'll be right with you.

00:27:37.761 --> 00:27:40.764
Don't they even have a menu?

00:27:40.847 --> 00:27:42.515
Here's the menu.

00:27:43.266 --> 00:27:45.810
Hey, I heard you're gay.

00:27:47.729 --> 00:27:49.397
I knew it, see?

00:27:49.481 --> 00:27:51.608
That's a soft ass!

00:27:56.404 --> 00:27:57.363
Are you gay too?

00:27:59.491 --> 00:28:02.702
Little gay, are you mad?

00:28:03.286 --> 00:28:05.580
No, I'm sorry, sir.

00:28:05.663 --> 00:28:07.957
Sir, I'm sorry.

00:28:08.041 --> 00:28:11.211
I'm sorry.

00:28:11.294 --> 00:28:13.338
Read the room!

00:28:18.009 --> 00:28:19.511
Johan, don't hit him!

00:28:19.594 --> 00:28:20.428
Go ahead. Hit me!

00:28:20.512 --> 00:28:22.889
Hit him, you bastard.

00:28:36.319 --> 00:28:38.780
You're seriously done for.

00:29:51.436 --> 00:29:52.770
"Former pro boxer

00:29:52.854 --> 00:29:58.443
causes violent incident at a gay bar
right after military discharge."

00:29:59.152 --> 00:30:01.237
Now that's a sensational headline, huh?

00:30:01.321 --> 00:30:02.906
Mr. Shim.

00:30:04.198 --> 00:30:06.242
Why are you here?

00:30:06.826 --> 00:30:09.120
I came to destroy your life.

00:30:12.582 --> 00:30:13.416
What?

00:30:16.502 --> 00:30:17.503
You leaked it.

00:30:19.964 --> 00:30:20.798
What?

00:30:20.882 --> 00:30:22.759
You leaked that stuff about me,
didn't you?!

00:30:23.551 --> 00:30:26.220
What are you talking about?

00:30:32.101 --> 00:30:33.853
Here! Over here!

00:30:34.354 --> 00:30:35.772
Right here.

00:30:37.065 --> 00:30:38.691
It's that guy in white.

00:30:39.400 --> 00:30:40.401
That one.

00:30:41.110 --> 00:30:43.363
No. No!

00:30:43.863 --> 00:30:45.114
It's not me. Mr. Shim.

00:30:45.198 --> 00:30:46.866
I'm not the one who leaked it!

00:30:48.576 --> 00:30:50.662
Mr. Shim! It wasn't me.

00:30:50.745 --> 00:30:53.081
It's not me!

00:30:53.164 --> 00:30:56.167
Wait, please. Mr. Shim!

00:33:07.757 --> 00:33:10.676
Subtitle translation by: Remi Miura